(firstQuint)Dopamine Agonist for Hemispatial Neglect and Motor Deficit Post Stroke.

 Hemispatial neglect and motor deficits remain major problems following right-hemisphere stroke.

 This study aims to assess the effect of rotigotine on hemispatial neglect, its component cognitive deficits (including spatial working memory and sustained attention) and motor deficits following right-hemisphere stroke.

